<div class="com-share" data-id="10620" data-title="《他俩搜罗了一群黑客和企业漏洞，然后做成了个大生意》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/10620/medium/10620.jpg?1436647033" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/10620.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
